---------------------------------------------------------------------
Crazy Diamond is a 1993 triple-CD boxed set of Syd Barrett's two 1970 
albums The Madcap Laughs and Barrett, and Opel, an out-takes compilation 
from 1988. All discs are further augmented by various alternate takes.

 Our main plan was to find Syd's acoustic takes, before the other musicians 
were drafted in to overdub them. But we stumbled across some fascinating 
material that sheds new light on Syd's working methods.
